seo: 微步在线,文件检测,反病毒引擎,威胁等级,病毒类型
seo_en: ThreatBook, file detection, anti-virus engine, threat level, malware type
summary: 该插件用于上传文件至微步在线进行反病毒引擎检测，并获取文件的威胁等级、是否为白名单文件、病毒类型、病毒家族及最近扫描时间等信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to upload files to ThreatBook for anti-virus engine detection, and obtain information such as threat level, whether it is a whitelist file, malware type, malware family, and the most recent scan time.
